snippet.title: PES Club Manager - official launch trailer
snippet.description: Konami today launched a new free-to-play mobile game, called PES Club Manager. In PES Club Manager, you can build up a team from the ground and control transfers and tactics. PES Club Manager includes a 3D match preview engine based on that of the PES 2015 console and PC versions.
